addUtility(address,uint8,bool).details: Nft contract must contain a <utilName()> corresponding to one of the dapps utility in LiquidStaking.

getRoleAdmin(bytes32).details: Returns the admin role that controls `role`. See {grantRole} and {revokeRole}. To change a role's admin, use {_setRoleAdmin}.

grantRole(bytes32,address).details: Grants `role` to `account`. If `account` had not been already granted `role`, emits a {RoleGranted} event. Requirements: - the caller must have ``role``'s admin role. May emit a {RoleGranted} event.

params.amounts: => array of amounts sended DNT tokens.
params.to: => address of the recipient. equals <address(0)> at burn.

renounceRole(bytes32,address).details: Revokes `role` from the calling account. Roles are often managed via {grantRole} and {revokeRole}: this function's purpose is to provide a mechanism for accounts to lose their privileges if they are compromised (such as when a trusted device is misplaced). If the calling account had been revoked `role`, emits a {RoleRevoked} event. Requirements: - the caller must be `account`. May emit a {RoleRevoked} event.

params.to: => address of the recipient. equals <address(0)> at burn.
=> address of the recipient. equals <address(0)> at burn.

params.era: => era in which to save new value.
=> era in which to save new fee.

multiTransferDnt(string[],address,addres.notice: function for redistribution of balances and fees for the user when multi-transferring DNT tokens.

removeManager(address).notice: function for removind <MANAGER> role to an account.

removeUtilityByAddress(address).notice: function for removing utility by nft contract address.

transferDnt(string,address,address,uint2.notice: function for redistribution of balances and fees for the user when transferring DNT tokens.

transferNft(string,address,address,uint2.notice: function for redistribution of balances and fees for the user when transferring nft.

updateUser(string,address,uint256,uint25.notice: function to update the user's balance in specified utility in specified era.
